  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Supporting Lender is a financial institution or individual providing support or funding, though specific details are not provided."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lender is a party involved in the restructuring and acquisition of securities for investment purposes."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lender is an organization that holds Claims and has the authority to vote, consent, and transfer these Claims."</data>
