  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Claims refer to financial obligations or rights that the Supporting Lender holds, which can include Prepetition Agreement Claims."&lt;SEP&gt;"Claims refer to potential legal claims that the Supporting Lender may have against the Company."</data>
