<node id="&quot;PREPETITION AGREEMENT CLAIMS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Prepetition Agreement Claims are claims that existed before the current agreement and are held through participations or interests or permissible transfers."&lt;SEP&gt;"Prepetition Agreement Claims refer to the claims related to the Prepetition Agreement, which Deerfield must collectively hold or control."</data>
