<node id="&quot;RESTRUCTURING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Restructuring is a process involving the modification or reorganization of the financial structure of a company or entity, as mentioned in the context of acquiring securities."&lt;SEP&gt;"Restructuring is a process mentioned in the agreement that is subject to conditions and judgments."&lt;SEP&gt;"Restructuring is a significant business action involving the Debtor, including asset sales and equity issuances, but excluding ordinary course of business activities."&lt;SEP&gt;"Restructuring is the process of modifying or reorganizing the financial structure of a company or entity, as mentioned in the context of acquiring securities."&lt;SEP&gt;"Restructuring refers to the process of reorganizing the financial structure of the Company."</data>
