</node>
<node id="&quot;AGREEMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Agreement is a document containing promises and mutual covenants and agreements between the parties."&lt;SEP&gt;"Agreement is a document that outlines the terms and conditions of the Material Contracts and other business agreements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Agreement is a formal document or arrangement that outlines the terms and conditions of a transaction or agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Agreement is the document containing the terms and conditions of the restructuring and other agreements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Agreement is the main document being executed, outlining the terms and conditions for the Supporting Lenders."&lt;SEP&gt;"Agreement is the main document containing the terms, conditions, and obligations of the parties involved."&lt;SEP&gt;"Agreement refers to a specific document or contract that outlines the terms of an agreement between parties."&lt;SEP&gt;"Agreement refers to the main contract or document that outlines the terms and conditions of the transaction."&lt;SEP&gt;"An Agreement is a formal document outlining terms and conditions of a transaction or negotiation."</data>
