  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Securities Act is a legal framework governing the issuance and sale of securities, defining terms like 'qualified institutional buyer' and 'institutional accredited investor'."&lt;SEP&gt;"Securities Act is a legal framework governing the issuance and sale of securities."&lt;SEP&gt;"Securities Act is a piece of legislation that regulates the offer and sale of securities in the United States."</data>
