<node id="&quot;COMPANY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Company is a business entity that engages in various operations, including beekeeping and lease agreements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is a business entity that has lease agreements and material contracts, and it is involved in beekeeping experience."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is another party to the agreement with specific covenants, representations, and warranties."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is another party to the agreement, also subject to covenants, representations, and warranties, and is responsible for notifications and compliance."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is the entity involved in the agreement and transactions, receiving information and making decisions based on the supporting lenders' actions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is the entity receiving information and documentation from the Supporting Lenders and its Affiliates."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to a business entity mentioned in the text, likely involved in some form of distribution or financial reporting."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to a business entity mentioned in the text, though specific details are not provided."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the entity that is filing the SEC documents and is subject to the compliance requirements mentioned."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the entity that provides notice to the Supporting Lenders and is involved in the termination events related to milestones and bankruptcy proceedings."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the main entity discussed in the text, which is involved in business operations and insurance policies."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the main entity involved in the agreement and its financial statements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the main entity involved in the transactions and agreements mentioned in the text."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the main entity mentioned in the text, responsible for filing documents with the SEC and performing obligations under various agreements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the main entity mentioned in the text, which has subsidiaries 