<node id="&quot;AFFILIATES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Affiliates are organizations that have a close association with the main Company, often sharing common ownership or management."&lt;SEP&gt;"Affiliates are related companies or entities associated with the Supporting Lenders."&lt;SEP&gt;"Affiliates are related companies or entities associated with the main company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Affiliates are related organizations or entities associated with the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Affiliates are related organizations or entities associated with the Supporting Lenders, providing additional context to the agreement."</data>
