<node id="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Supporting Lenders are entities that retain professionals for various purposes related to an agreement and related transactions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions or entities that are part of an agreement, providing support and making certain disclaimers regarding the accuracy of information provided."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions or entities that have agreed to certain terms and conditions, such as consenting to the Key Employee Incentive Plan and Key Employee Retention Plan."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions or entities that provide financial support or loans."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions or entities that provide support or funding for certain transactions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions or entities that provide support to the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions or entities that support the Company in some capacity, though specific details are not provided."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are parties to an agreement with certain covenants, representations, and warranties, and are subject to conditions and breaches."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are parties to the agreement with specific covenants, representations, and warranties."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are the entities that receive notices from the Company and are involved in providing extensions and claims related to the Prepetition Agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are the entities to whom the Company has provided financial statements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are the parties providing support or financing to the Company as mentioned in the agreement."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-477586aae31575a2d4579dd1dd4e5e38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0a7f06cdfef313832757561409e1f2e2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19cc232c450902b9e868c6fdfd3aa6b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d78695ccc70fed837b2a4c729251120&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac8810aa347bb9046a5ebb7bb3c8da29&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d49561091ac27f1b0af51d94fd414636&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-299789486a6981e730a051b5b7613219&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ec30e257221e71c474d6266d0784c302&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8b6ac77e35b3b903663ad7dc1150e984&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-272024f9438dbb1eb8f8eb69b27c343b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47ce6f0b5e366ac7fd52736461b1b43f</data>
