<node id="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Subsidiaries are affiliated companies owned or controlled by the main Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are affiliated companies under the same parent company as the Company, also involved in lease agreements and material contracts."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are affiliated organizations under the Company, sharing similar contractual and financial responsibilities."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are affiliated organizations under the same parent company as the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are subsidiary companies of the main Company, mentioned in the context of financial reporting and tax matters."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are subsidiary companies owned by the main company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are subsidiary organizations of the Company, possibly involved in the transactions and subject to the same conditions as the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are subsidiary organizations of the main Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are subsidiary organizations under the Company, which may also be subject to taxation."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-477586aae31575a2d4579dd1dd4e5e38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72a8869b8a35f37ec389834d0871ab40&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32603276a52db27e454f08ff7a05e930&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-299789486a6981e730a051b5b7613219&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fbd91217ca62380da07abc8b84cfd236&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8b6ac77e35b3b903663ad7dc1150e984&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc244d1acb3b90b71ad2ddec98df51b1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-678eb9108a7643fb7533cf8ebd731a1b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a6f0c8b641c5362496d9135cd0b32820</data>
