<node id="&quot;CANNON&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Cannon is a biologist who emphasized the importance of regulation in physiology and medicine."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cannon is a person who proposed theories about regulation in the body and physiology, emphasizing the role of regulatory factors in maintaining homeostasis."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cannon is a physiologist known for his work on homeostatic mechanisms and their implications for medicine."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cannon is a researcher who introduced the concept of homeostasis and conducted extensive physiological research over three decades."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cannon is a scientist who studied the body's ability to maintain critical functions within narrow ranges, combining his knowledge of digestion, respiration, heart rate, and responses to stress in animals."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cannon was a physiologist who contributed significantly to the understanding of homeostatic mechanisms and their implications for medicine."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b7d9d5fbedb55c3eb193d14294704df3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-11676ae8259d9bef41b4ab8ba19335b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-06b4a9642d883a25a7c071da2debc224&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fb7df499a97264ccc13db5f384907372&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3d1f018f894ed3aab36e02fad8d45d76&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0dff7ef5962f43b369673f95ef8d49a3</data>
