<node id="&quot;CHOLESTEROL&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Cholesterol is a substance that is linked to heart disease and is the target of Endo's research."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cholesterol is a type of lipid that is crucial for cell function, with two forms: LDL (bad cholesterol) and HDL (good cholesterol)."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cholesterol is a type of lipid that plays a crucial role in cell membrane structure and hormone production, and its levels can affect cellular processes."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cholesterol is the substance whose synthesis Endo aimed to inhibit with a fungal compound."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-7abd72e28bd44e36a5eeb7b2c8e5cff0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ec30e257221e71c474d6266d0784c302&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9aca1081bd8725c55ba60d9e4688ccff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7fc7e5ee15c5a83367a5f243f4eb6664</data>
