</node>
<node id="&quot;LDL RECEPTOR&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"LDL Receptor is a protein that binds to low-density lipoprotein (LDL), allowing cells to take up cholesterol from the bloodstream."&lt;SEP&gt;"LDL receptor is a protein that helps cells absorb LDL cholesterol from the bloodstream."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-7abd72e28bd44e36a5eeb7b2c8e5cff0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ec30e257221e71c474d6266d0784c302</data>
