</node>
<node id="&quot;REDUCTASE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Reductase is an enzyme that catalyzes the reduction of molecules, often in the synthesis of cholesterol."&lt;SEP&gt;"Reductase is an enzyme that plays a role in cholesterol synthesis within cells."&lt;SEP&gt;"Reductase is the enzyme in the cholesterol pathway that Endo targeted with his tests."&lt;SEP&gt;"Reductase is the target of Endo's later research, specifically the enzyme that synthesizes cholesterol."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-7abd72e28bd44e36a5eeb7b2c8e5cff0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ec30e257221e71c474d6266d0784c302&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9aca1081bd8725c55ba60d9e4688ccff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7fc7e5ee15c5a83367a5f243f4eb6664</data>
