</node>
<node id="&quot;CELLS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Cells are the basic units of life and are responsible for maintaining homeostasis, including cholesterol levels."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cells are the basic units of life that maintain cholesterol levels through various mechanisms such as drawing cholesterol from the bloodstream and synthesizing it."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-7abd72e28bd44e36a5eeb7b2c8e5cff0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ec30e257221e71c474d6266d0784c302</data>
