</node>
<node id="&quot;NUC&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Nuc is a functioning bee colony, typically used for starting new hives, containing a laying queen and initial resources."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-6e8e292472440147bfd5caa5df68f872</data>
