<node id="&quot;PACKAGE COLONY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Package Colony is another type of bee colony, often used for starting new hives, consisting of a group of worker bees with a queen."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-6e8e292472440147bfd5caa5df68f872</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 12}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 75}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 127}]</data>
