<node id="&quot;COMMERCIAL BEEKEEPERS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Commercial Beekeepers refer to businesses that maintain and manage honeybee colonies for the production of honey and other bee products."&lt;SEP&gt;"Commercial Beekeepers use the so-called migratory cover, a style of hive that has no overhang on the sides and often none on the front and back, allowing for hives to be packed more tightly when loading them on a truck."&lt;SEP&gt;"Commercial beekeepers use the so-called migratory cover, a style of hive that has no overhang on the sides and often none on the front and back, allowing for hives to be packed more tightly when loading them on a truck."</data>
