</node>
<node id="&quot;BEE SPACE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bee Space is the necessary gap between combs and frames within a beehive to allow bees to move freely and maintain the structure of the hive."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-5332ab7934f0ae27f98ce704b12255df</data>
</node>
