  <data key="d1">"Cypress is a type of wood available from some sources for making wooden hive parts in beekeeping."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-b0630edb5f2e5f736478f6d764392a08</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BOTTOM BOARD&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bottom board is a component of a beehive that supports the lowermost box and provides an entrance for the bees."&lt;SEP&gt;"The bottom board is a component of the hive stand that sits on the ground, protecting the hive from moisture and supporting the hive structure."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-06b4a9642d883a25a7c071da2debc224&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0630edb5f2e5f736478f6d764392a08</data>
