</node>
<node id="&quot;HIVE BODIES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Hive bodies are the main boxes of a beehive that house the brood nest and stores honey."&lt;SEP&gt;"Hive bodies are the main components of the beehive structure, providing space for the bees to live and store honey."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-7b9cfa85a9917b7e3e3663f39bc8090b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0630edb5f2e5f736478f6d764392a08</data>
