  <data key="d1">"Softwoods are a type of wood known for their lighter weight and softer texture compared to hardwoods, often used in construction and other applications."&lt;SEP&gt;"Softwoods are types of wood commonly used in hive construction due to their lighter weight and lower cost compared to hardwoods."</data>
