  <data key="d2">chunk-11676ae8259d9bef41b4ab8ba19335b2</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BODY FUNCTIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Body Functions refer to various physiological processes that Cannon studied and aimed to understand in terms of homeostasis."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-11676ae8259d9bef41b4ab8ba19335b2</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 2}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 34}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;REGULATORY MECHANISMS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Regulatory Mechanisms are the mechanisms Cannon identified as maintaining steady states in the body, as part of his concept of homeostasis."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-11676ae8259d9bef41b4ab8ba19335b2</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 2}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 37}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;THE WISDOM OF THE BODY&quot;">
