  <data key="d2">chunk-11676ae8259d9bef41b4ab8ba19335b2</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 2}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 33}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;EXTERNAL DISTURBANCES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"External Disturbances are factors that Cannon considered in his research on how the body maintains homeostasis."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-11676ae8259d9bef41b4ab8ba19335b2</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 2}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 37}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ACID-BASE BALANCE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Acid-Base Balance is a specific example of a state maintained through regulatory mechanisms, as mentioned by Cannon."</data>
