<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">78.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company relies on the Supporting Lenders for information and guidance, indicating a direct relationship."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders and Company are both parties to the agreement, with conditions and breaches affecting each other."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders make disclaimers regarding the accuracy of information provided to the Company, indicating a contractual relationship."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company has obligations towards the Supporting Lenders as detailed in the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company provides notices to the Supporting Lenders regarding milestones and termination events."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company seeks support from Supporting Lenders, though the nature of this support is not specified."</data>
