  <data key="d4">26.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supporting Lenders seek Bankruptcy Court approval for administrative expense priority claims."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Supporting Lenders can file motions or pleadings with the Bankruptcy Court that may be inconsistent with the agreement."</data>
