<edge source="&quot;CHOLESTEROL&quot;" target="&quot;CONCEPT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Cholesterol levels affect cellular processes, including the activity of LDL receptors and reductase."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ec30e257221e71c474d6266d0784c302</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CHOLESTEROL&quot;" target="&quot;ENDO&quot;">
  <data key="d4">27.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Cholesterol is the substance whose synthesis Endo aimed to inhibit with a fungal compound."&lt;SEP&gt;"Endo focused on developing drugs to combat high cholesterol after identifying a parasitic fungus that could make the right enzymes."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-9aca1081bd8725c55ba60d9e4688ccff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7fc7e5ee15c5a83367a5f243f4eb6664</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CHOLESTEROL&quot;" target="&quot;FUNGI&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Fungi produce compounds that can inhibit cholesterol synthesis, as Endo reasoned in his research."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-9aca1081bd8725c55ba60d9e4688ccff</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;LDL RECEPTOR&quot;" target="&quot;CONCEPT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"LDL Receptor binds to LDL in the bloodstream, allowing cells to take up cholesterol."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ec30e257221e71c474d6266d0784c302</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;REDUCTASE&quot;" target="&quot;CONCEPT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Reductase is involved in the synthesis of cholesterol, which is influenced by cholesterol levels."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ec30e257221e71c474d6266d0784c302</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;REDUCTASE&quot;" target="&quot;ENDO&quot;">
  <data key="d4">38.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Endo targeted the reductase enzyme in the cholesterol pathway with his tests."&lt;SEP&gt;"Endo's later research was directed towards inhibitors of cholesterol synthesis, specifically targeting reductase."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-9aca1081bd8725c55ba60d9e4688ccff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7fc7e5ee15c5a83367a5f243f4eb6664</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;REDUCTASE&quot;" target="&quot;SANKYO PHARMACEUTICAL COMPANY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Sankyo pharmaceutical company was researching inhibitors of cholesterol synthesis, specifically targeting reductase."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-9aca1081bd8725c55ba60d9e4688ccff</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CELLS&quot;" target="&quot;CONCEPT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Cells maintain their cholesterol levels through the action of LDL receptors and reductase."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ec30e257221e71c474d6266d0784c302</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BLOODSTREAM&quot;" target="&quot;CONCEPT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bloodstream carries LDL to cells, which can be influenced by cholesterol levels."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ec30e257221e71c474d6266d0784c302</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;LDL&quot;" target="&quot;CONCEPT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"LDL is a carrier of cholesterol in the bloodstream, which can affect cellular processes."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ec30e257221e71c474d6266d0784c302</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;MONOPOLIZATION&quot;" target="&quot;CONCEPT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Monopolization is prohibited by antitrust laws, which regulate mergers and acquisitions."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ec30e257221e71c474d6266d0784c302</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;RESTRAINT OF TRADE&quot;" target="&quot;CONCEPT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Restraint of Trade is prohibited by antitrust laws, which regulate mergers and acquisitions."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ec30e257221e71c474d6266d0784c302</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;LESSENING COMPETITION&quot;" target="&quot;CONCEPT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Lessening Competition is prohibited by antitrust laws, which regulate mergers and acquisitions."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ec30e257221e71c474d6266d0784c302</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPRANATIONAL&quot;" target="&quot;CONCEPT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supranational laws can influence antitrust regulations across multiple countries."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ec30e257221e71c474d6266d0784c302</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
