  <data key="d4">30.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Both returnable and throw-away boxes are used to transport a Nucleus Hive (nuc), though the returnable box is reusable while the throw-away box is not."&lt;SEP&gt;"Both throw-away and returnable boxes are used to transport a Nucleus Hive (nuc), though the returnable box is reusable while the throw-away box is not."</data>
