  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Nuc is housed in a Single-story Hive, providing a specific environment for the bees to live and produce honey."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-6e8e292472440147bfd5caa5df68f872</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PACKAGE&quot;" target="&quot;QUEEN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Package contains the necessary components, including the queen, to ensure the successful integration of the Nucleus Hive (nuc) into the existing hive structure."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-eec9462a5adf7ec8d10f626e103389f3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PACKAGE&quot;" target="&quot;BROOD&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Package includes the necessary components, including brood, to ensure the successful integration of the Nucleus Hive (nuc) into the existing hive structure, providing a foundation for the new colony."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-eec9462a5adf7ec8d10f626e103389f3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PACKAGE&quot;" target="&quot;HIVE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Package is installed in the Hive to facilitate the integration of the Nucleus Hive (nuc) into the existing hive structure, ensuring a smooth transition for the new colony."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-eec9462a5adf7ec8d10f626e103389f3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PACKAGE&quot;" target="&quot;FRAMES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Package includes the necessary components, including frames, to ensure the successful integration of the Nucleus Hive (nuc) into the existing hive structure, providing essential resources for the colony."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-eec9462a5adf7ec8d10f626e103389f3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PACKAGE&quot;" target="&quot;POLLEN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Package includes the necessary components, including pollen, to ensure the successful integration of the Nucleus Hive (nuc) into the existing hive structure, supporting the colony's nutrition needs."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-eec9462a5adf7ec8d10f626e103389f3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PACKAGE&quot;" target="&quot;HONEY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Package includes the necessary components, including honey, to ensure the successful integration of the Nucleus Hive (nuc) into the existing hive structure, supporting the colony's nutrition needs."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-eec9462a5adf7ec8d10f626e103389f3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PACKAGE&quot;" target="&quot;ADULT BEES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Package includes the necessary components, including adult bees, to ensure the successful integration of the Nucleus Hive (nuc) into the existing hive structure, providing essential labor for the colony."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-eec9462a5adf7ec8d10f626e103389f3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PACKAGE&quot;" target="&quot;COLONY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Package includes the necessary components, including the queen, brood, frames, pollen, honey, and adult bees, to ensure the successful integration of the Nucleus Hive (nuc) into the existing hive structure, forming a cohesive unit within the larger hive structure."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-eec9462a5adf7ec8d10f626e103389f3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PACKAGE&quot;" target="&quot;PROBLEM&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Package can lead to a Problem if the queen is not accepted by the existing bees in the hive, causing issues with the integration of the Nucleus Hive (nuc)."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-eec9462a5adf7ec8d10f626e103389f3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PACKAGE&quot;" target="&quot;INSTALLATION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Package is a critical component of the Installation process, which is essential for the successful integration of the Nucleus Hive (nuc) into the existing hive structure."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-eec9462a5adf7ec8d10f626e103389f3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;QUEEN&quot;" target="&quot;BROOD&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Queen is responsible for laying eggs that develop into Brood, ensuring the continuous growth and health of the Nucleus Hive (nuc)."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-eec9462a5adf7ec8d10f626e103389f3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;QUEEN&quot;" target="&quot;HIVE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Queen is a crucial part of the Hive, laying eggs and ensuring the overall health and productivity of the colony within the Nucleus Hive (nuc)."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-eec9462a5adf7ec8d10f626e103389f3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;QUEEN&quot;" target="&quot;FRAMES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Queen is responsible for laying eggs that develop into Brood, which are stored in Frames, ensuring the continuous growth and health of the Nucleus Hive (nuc)."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-eec9462a5adf7ec8d10f626e103389f3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;QUEEN&quot;" target="&quot;POLLEN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Queen's presence and the resulting Brood help ensure the availability of Pollen, a vital food source for the colony within the Nucleus Hive (nuc)."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-eec9462a5adf7ec8d10f626e103389f3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;QUEEN&quot;" target="&quot;HONEY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Queen's presence and the resulting Brood help ensure the availability of Honey, a vital food source for the colony within the Nucleus Hive (nuc)."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-eec9462a5adf7ec8d10f626e103389f3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
