  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Nuc is housed in a Hive, providing shelter and space for the bees to live and produce honey."&lt;SEP&gt;"Nuc is housed in a hive, providing shelter and space for the bees."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-6e8e292472440147bfd5caa5df68f872</data>
