  <data key="d4">4.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The period from 1735 to 1864 saw the emergence of forms like extravaganza, which influenced the development of American musical theater."&lt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-289a23908915c5bcd0308dffe4b44213</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
